data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. There’s no reason to spend time or effort to build a brand-new home when you can buy this magnificent home now! This recently built home, built in 2020, will leave you stunned with its beauty and its location. Located in Riverview Tampa, take in all the beautiful lakes and bodies of water while also being close to great schools and many shopping centers filled with stores and restaurants. The home is in the majestic neighborhood of South Fork, you must come see all the lakes, ponds, and enjoy the ginormous community pool. Entering the home, you will be greeted with the long foyer which can lead you to the living room or to several bedrooms, all of which are delightful. Once you walk to the living room take in the open floor plan filled with sunlight to fill you with peace. The kitchen is also spacious and offers the same great views as the living room. Steeping outside to the patio, be amazed at the wide plain of grass at your disposal all surrounded by a vinyl fence. From the living room you can enter the master bedroom, take in its grandeur with its massive space and the great masted bathroom. The three bedrooms connected to the foyer are great for any family! What are you waiting for? Make this home yours before someone else does!
